### Note on Categories:
# Categories are dynamic and will be created automatically when new items are added
# Some suggested categories as examples:
# - Kursi (Chairs)
# - Meja (Tables)
# - Komputer (Computers)
# - Printer
# - Power Generator
# - Power Supply
# - Network Equipment
# - Storage
# - Electronics
# But you can create any new category as needed!

