GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/transactions

### Get Transaction by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/transactions/1

### Get Transaction by Reference
GET {{baseUrl}}/inventory/transactions/reference/PO%2F2024%2F001
